_time_low":569.05,"long_business_summary":"Mobavenue AI Tech Limited operates AI-powered advertising, marketing, and consumer media platforms in India. The company offers digital media and advertising agency services, including digital marketing, content creation, mobile advertising, IT solutions, and related consulting services. It also offers OrbitX, an AI-powered search and contextual advertising platform, and EarnX, an ad monetization platform. In addition, the company offers computer applications, IT solutions, technical consulting, and support services related to software, data networks, and systems integration. Further, it provides advertising services, including audio-visual media, digital media, and mobile content. The company was formerly known as Lucent Industries Limited and changed its name to Mobavenue AI Tech Limited in October 2025. Mobavenue AI Tech Limited was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}